OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable amounts of cloud and
OL,6,Foutbreaks of patchy light rain
OL,7,Fthroughout the day. However, there
OL,8,Fwill be occasional bright or sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Breezy along the coasts.
OL,10,FTemperatures around average, but
OL,11,Ffeeling cool in the breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy with further outbreaks
OL,14,Fof showery rain this evening, although
OL,15,Fthese easing to leave a largely dry
OL,16,Fnight, with some clear spells
OL,17,Fdeveloping. Turning locally chilly,
OL,18,Fwith light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
