OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA band of rain will be moving
OL,6,Fsoutheast across all parts during
OL,7,FFriday afternoon, with some showers
OL,8,Fdeveloping ahead of this, these could
OL,9,Fbe locally heavy. Breezy. Temperatures
OL,10,Fnear normal.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA band
OL,13,Fof rain continues to move south on
OL,14,FSaturday. Breezy. Fine and dry with
OL,15,Fsunny spells and light winds on
OL,16,FSunday. Sunny spells and showers on
OL,17,FMonday. Feeling cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
